2 Data processing

dat_sf <- st_read("./data/glacier_clim.shp")
## Reading layer `glacier_clim' from data source `/Users/u0784726/Dropbox/Data/devtools/glacier_mb/data/glacier_clim.shp' using driver `ESRI Shapefile'
## Simple feature collection with 95086 features and 25 fields
## Geometry type: POINT
## Dimension:     XY
## Bounding box:  xmin: 67.47845 ymin: 27.4918 xmax: 103.8915 ymax: 45.35089
## Geodetic CRS:  GCS_unknown
dat_sf <- dat_sf[sample(1:nrow(dat_sf), 5000), ]

dat <- dat_sf %>%
  st_drop_geometry() %>% 
  dplyr::select(mb_mwea, area_km2, z_min, z_med, z_max, z_aspct, z_slope,
                east, north, tau,
                t2m_18, t2m_d, tp_18, tp_d)

2.1 Scaling

dat <- dat %>%
  mutate(area_km2 = scale(area_km2),
         z_med = scale(z_med),
         z_aspct = scale(z_aspct),
         z_slope = scale(z_slope),
         tau = scale(tau),
         t2m_d = scale(t2m_d),
         tp_d = scale(tp_d)
  )

2.2 INLA spatial graph

dat$idarea <- 1:nrow(dat)

# crds <- st_coordinates(dat)
coo <- cbind(dat$east / 1000,
             dat$north / 1000)

nb <- graph2nb(gabrielneigh(coo), sym = TRUE)

nb2INLA("map.adj", nb)
g <- inla.read.graph("map.adj")

3 INLA model

Priors

prior_bym <- list(prec.unstruct=list(prior='pc.prec',param=c(1, 0.025)),
                  prec.spatial=list(prior='pc.prec', param=c(1, 0.025)))
f1 <- mb_mwea ~ t2m_d + tp_d + 
  z_med + z_slope + z_aspct + 
  tau + area_km2 +
  f(idarea, model = "bym", graph = g, hyper = prior_bym)

system.time(
  res1 <- inla(f1, data = dat,
               control.predictor = list(compute = TRUE),
               control.compute = list(dic = TRUE, waic = TRUE))
)
## Warning in .recacheSubclasses(def@className, def, env): undefined subclass
## "numericVector" of class "Mnumeric"; definition not updated

3.2 Obs vs pred

plot_df <- data.frame(obs = dat$mb_mwea,
                      pred = res1$summary.fitted.values$mean)
ggplot(plot_df, aes(x = obs, y = pred)) +
  geom_point()

3.3 Map spatial effect

spatial_re <- res1$summary.random$idarea
dat_sf$re <- spatial_re$mean[1:nrow(dat_sf)]
m1 <- tm_shape(dat_sf) +
  tm_symbols(col = "re", size = 0.25, alpha = 0.75, style = "quantile") 
print(m1)

dat_sf$yhat <- plot_df$pred
m2 <- tm_shape(dat_sf) +
  tm_symbols(col = "yhat", size = 0.25, alpha = 0.75, style = "quantile") 
print(m2)

4 Interaction example

f2 <- mb_mwea ~ t2m_d * t2m_18 + tp_d + 
  z_slope + z_aspct + z_med + 
  tau + area_km2 +
  f(idarea, model = "bym", graph = g, hyper = prior_bym)

system.time(
  res2 <- inla(f2, data = dat,
               control.predictor = list(compute = TRUE),
               control.compute = list(dic = TRUE, waic = TRUE))
)
